title.en-US: Become a Sales Expert and Launch Your Remote Career

text.en-US: Learn a highly in-demand profession which allows you to work from anywhere in the world in 8 weeks (full-time) or 16 weeks (part-time).

text_1.en-US: Become a Sales Representative, Business Developer or an Account Manager, roles which every company needs.

text_2.en-US: Learn technical skills to build landing pages or newsletters, master solutions used by sales experts in today’s companies such as LinkedIn Sales Navigator, chatbot and automated sales funnels.

text_3.en-US: We limit class sizes to a maximum of 10 people to ensure you have the best learning experience.

text_4.en-US: Since the program is built in partnership with companies you will have the chance to meet some of our partners looking to recruit.

text.en-US: We partnered with tech companies, start-ups and online business owners from all over the world to build the program and help you launch your first Sales Remote Job.

checkboxLabel_1_a.en-US: From Monday to Friday, all day (2h break).

title.en-US: We built the program together with start-ups and tech companies.

text.en-US: We partnered with tech companies, start-ups and online business owners from all over the world to build the program and help you launch your first Sales Remote Job.

text_1.en-US: We present your CV and profile to leading tech companies and startups.

text_2.en-US: During the course, you will meet people who have already achieved what you’re aiming for.

text_3.en-US: Senior sales experts participate in the program to share the real world insights and prepare you for success.

text_4.en-US: We negotiate with companies and help our students get remote internships from partnered companies.

paragraph_1.en-US: There is a lack of digital-native sales professionals in the market, while the continued growth of technology creates a high demand for Sales Experts that can find new customers. According to a LinkedIn report, Sales Representative roles are the most in-demand jobs with a 34% annual growth.

paragraph_2.en-US: In this bootcamp, you will learn from experts working with tech companies and startups based in US and Europe. The program is built to allow you to acquire both soft and hard skills, but also to prepare you to become successful as a remote worker.

title.en-US: A new generation of sales professionals

paragraph_a.en-US: Univertop is an online bootcamp which trains the new generation of sales professionals and business developers in methodologies and digital tools. By the end of this program, you will be skilled in the sales process, know how to plan a winning sales strategy, and implement inbound and outbound leads generation (phone, email, social media channels).

paragraph_b.en-US: You’ll also learn how to nurture existing customers, gather clients’ requirements, prepare sales proposals, and manage contracts. Plus, you’ll gain knowledge on how to manage the sales cycle and documentation in the CRM and other online sales platforms.

paragraph_1.en-US: Joining the bootcamp also means you get to join an inspiring global sales community that includes people who are also reinventing their life by working from home or becoming a digital nomad. This network is crucial when it comes to career growth and finding support. This is why our students get lifetime access to the alumni database and may refer to one another for professional opportunities.

paragraph_2.en-US: Remote working is a dream which requires a lot of organisation and particular skills. The bootcamp will teach you effective skills and communication, which is quite different when working remotely, as well as tools to manage priorities, online meetings etc.

cardText_1.en-US: 100% of interactive live online training led by Sales Experts. Our online courses are given live to ensure real-time learning and easy communication between students and mentors. We also limit class sizes to ensure you have the best learning experience!

cardTitle_2.en-US: Raise your chances of being hired

cardText_2.en-US: Because this profession can only be learned through practice, each student has a dedicated project to help boost sales for a start-up, e-commerce, digital entrepreneur, or tech company. It is a great opportunity to study and apply new skills directly.

cardTitle_3.en-US: Increase your chances of getting a remote job

cardText_3.en-US: The program includes career advice, help to optimize your resume, and support in creating an online profile and personal branding strategy. This will raise your chances of being hired or support you in finding work and clients as a freelancer. We also help our students be recruited by our partner companies.
